      • StaticPartitioningStatistics

        public StaticPartitioningStatistics(ChocoReconfigurationAlgorithmParams ps,
                                    int n,
                                    int v,
                                    int c,
                                    long st,
                                    long sd,
                                    long d,
                                    int w,
                                    int nbParts)
        Make the statistics.
        Parameters:
        ps - the standard parameters for the solving process
        n - the number of nodes in the model
        v - the number of VMs in the model
        c - the number of satisfaction-oriented constraints.
        st - the moment the computation started, epoch format
        sd - the duration of the splitting process in milliseconds
        d - the solving process duration in milliseconds
        w - the number of workers to solve the partitions in parallel
        nbParts - the number of partitions to compute
